We were alerted to this issue by our monitoring system and addressed this issue by rolling back our software update. We sincerely apologize for the inconvenience caused by this issue. We take this issue seriously and have identified several improvements in our software rollout procedure which will help us avoid these issues in future. We will be changing our rollout procedure accordingly.
